{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 exercise. After participating in numerous meetings with your colleagues and after drafting, critiquing, and revising many drafts, you produce four different documents:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
